  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Tibial Tray Fixation Stress Credibility Assessment (NC-4 Clean)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for finite-element prediction of tibial tray interface stress in a cemented total knee arthroplasty (TKA) system under physiological gait loading. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can predict peak cement-bone interface stress within ±15% of experimental values at Model Risk Level 3. All 13 credibility factors are assessed; achieved levels meet or exceed required levels. Decision: Accepted.",
